            "title": "恒指新貴揚升   洛鉬曾升逾7.6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指新貴表現理想，其中洛陽鉬業(03993)表現最佳，曾升7.64%，見23.38元，現升7.55%，報23.36元，成交1.42億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"洛陽鉬業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03993-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"洛陽鉬業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03993-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">洛陽鉬業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">老鋪黃金(06181)最高見783.5元，升6..09%，現升4.94%，報775元，成交4.94元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">寧德時代(03750)升2.22%，報529元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">出局的中升控股(00881)跌2.79%，報11.85元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指季檢加入洛陽鉬業、老鋪黃金及寧德時代，剔出中升控股，成份股數目由88隻增至90隻。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數無改變。</p>\n</div>",
